title: EXPLAINING JOSH’S OLD RELATIONSHIP TO WALLO & GILLIE — BFFs EP. 47 W/ MILLION DOLLAZ WORTH OF GAME
description:
This week, we're joined by fellow Barstool podcasters Gillie and Wallo from Million Dollaz Worth Of Game to introduce them to Josh and the world of TikTok. We run through this week's headlines including Kylie Jenner and Lil Nas X both being pregnant, what happened with Addison Rae and the pod, and the rumored Olivia Ponton/Kai split.
